To install Wikidot Open Source follow the points:

0. Install PostgreSQL, PHP, Lighttpd
1. Prepare a PostgreSQL database.

$ su postgres
$ make prepare_db
$ exit

2. Install Wikidot db.

$ make

3. Run Wikidot

$ ./wikidotctl start

4. Go to the URL make prints at the end to configure your wiki superuser password.

> http://127.0.0.1:8080/admin:superadmin/key/...